{"tid":992180,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得08奧運體操選手江鈺源","createTime":"2019-01-23T03:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T07:12:55.000Z","uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"023dedd0ebdb81652cd136077392e3ac10d6740b","tid":992180,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:28:50.000Z","msg":"中國體操女神江鈺源　被爆色誘閨密老公<br />\n<br />\n中國女子體操隊一向予人美貌與實力兼備的感覺，08年北京奧運中國隊首奪女子團體金牌，成員之一江鈺源正是其中一位代表。去年碩士畢業的江鈺源一直被網民譽為「大眼美女」，不過近日卻捲入一宗桃色醜聞，有人大爆她甘做「小三」色誘有婦之夫，設計拆散對方家庭，而且原配更是江鈺源的閨密！爆料者公開江鈺源「超淫賤對話」及偷情證據，並表明「陸續有來」，暗示有2人床照隨時曝光，震撼中國體壇！ <br />\n<br />\n日前有名為「海洋律師LAW」的網民在微博爆料：「體操奧運冠軍當小三，插足破壞閨密家庭，色誘洗腦海歸男，砸錢，布局設套，栽贓陷害閨密猛潑髒水只為逼其主動離婚！實錘、實錘、實錘！先上前菜，續有猛料。」該爆料者暗示「猛料」包括「各種18禁姿勢」，似乎預告將有床照曝光，而且爆料者現時公開的「前菜」，包括疑似江鈺源與有婦之夫的淫賤對話，亦足夠成為近日中國體壇最熱門話題。 <br />\n<br />\n爆料者公開的微信對話截圖中，江鈺源的名字為「xsjyy」，意思為「小三江鈺源」，微信內容極之露骨大膽，包括「等着我去強姦你」、「射嘴裏」等等，又教對方要「先拖着，她着急了會來跟你離婚」。爆料者同時公開了江鈺源的機票，時間、地點均與微信心對話吻合，並有一張疑似為江鈺源的裸背照。 <br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：【江鈺源乖女形象破滅　曾同陳一冰拍拖】 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2R42xYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2R42xYA&d=PD6BU5FT0PaiJLYkH2SYQttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5f5c4cd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2R42xYA</a>　 <br />\n<br />\n網民發現，閨密身份為廣東體操隊女教練唐健，她曾於2017年11月1日(江鈺源生日)在微博發文：「小三今天是你的生日，希望你能學會行為檢點，我們的事還沒完呢，勸你夾起尾巴做人，別沒完沒了挑戰我的底線。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QuZT3Sh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQuZT3Sh.png&h=e0c2baf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0nqUZd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0nqUZd.png&h=e2bccb42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d161f44b9bcc091cfc5221a9883cbe2a42123943","tid":992180,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:30:40.000Z","msg":"床照呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc8967f1c8a1f9b6b2b9ebe4444226f6f09cde2","tid":992180,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:31:39.000Z","msg":"係幾靚<br />\n可惜 雞 全部都係雞.JPG <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0127a86d51513f86e671d62fae0f888e4b6f456c","tid":992180,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:23:59.000Z","msg":"上樑不正下樑歪,成個國家都係咁<br />\n<br />\n司法界掀淫亂醜聞 律師「定期送處女」討好大法官<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/989241/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/989241/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"df32068582c9e62b5bfc239510b8e7d1c16a4e6d","tid":992180,"uid":59242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:13:38.000Z","msg":"可以花式屌閪，咩pose 都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67363834a6385d749d02ec93ea0488077b22e5c6","tid":992180,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:37:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a339775cd405d00f5b22716daf1ebf10cade327b","tid":992180,"uid":139082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:47:53.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯komova正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fd5176924e5faa5a75d0f1b609ffddc71a7f9e","tid":992180,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a339775cd405d00f5b22716daf1ebf10cade327b","tid":992180,"uid":139082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:47:53.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯komova正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:53:25.000Z","msg":"有冇近照睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daca47a8b642e3308d7f761efbd3436d8b5f4a41","tid":992180,"uid":75394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:58:33.000Z","msg":"komova越大越樣衰<br />\nMustafina生咗個重keep得好好"},{"pid":"b04afb0c8defb9e1b57444